{"tid":2375181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"強國男不慎把24cmx6cm玻璃瓶塞進後門　醫生撐開菊花向外拉順利取出","createTime":"2021-01-21T23:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T10:48:55.000Z","uid":204533,"like":189,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"d7b5686413d539078e9d42098908c5fe79c11722","tid":2375181,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"近日，家住河南駐馬店市平輿縣的老畢，不慎將一個24cm&times;6cm大小的玻璃瓶塞入肛門，在家中苦苦努力一夜，不但沒把玻璃瓶取出，反而導致玻璃瓶越陷越深的情況下，被家人送往駐馬店市中心醫院肛腸科。醫生檢查後發現老畢的肛門不僅出現了明顯水腫，更可怕的是手指已經觸摸不到玻璃瓶；這意味著，單從肛門取出玻璃瓶的可能性微乎其微。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/OnmlAWtxyMqGFpbu2zWKMmhG1zk=/760x879/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XEIJJPZ6J5G45I2MO3YVZLKQGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOnmlAWtxyMqGFpbu2zWKMmhG1zk%3D%2F760x879%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXEIJJPZ6J5G45I2MO3YVZLKQGA.jpg&h=c75ac07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終，經過和家屬溝通協調，制定手術方案，商定在麻醉醫師的配合下，先自肛門處小心嘗試取出異物，如果取出困難，立刻為患者實施開腹手術，自腹部取出異物。在麻醉科手術部的密切配合下，由團隊中手尺寸最小的副主任醫師自肛門探查玻璃瓶的大概位置，發現玻璃瓶位於直腸乙狀結腸交界處，隨後在患者腹部輕柔擠壓腸管，將玻璃瓶緩慢推向直腸末端。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/t1T5wa63vXTEZv2uK1DA-P3USiw=/760x903/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZYLGCMW5WFBB3FHBHHC3TQHH7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft1T5wa63vXTEZv2uK1DA-P3USiw%3D%2F760x903%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZYLGCMW5WFBB3FHBHHC3TQHH7U.jpg&h=e91e40f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一組醫生透過肛門撐開器將患者的肛門撐開，觸摸到玻璃瓶後，用手術器械將其輕柔地向外牽拉，數名醫生上下其手，一起發力，歷經一個多小將其成功取出，避免了開腹手術，減輕了患者的創傷。術後第二天，老畢的不適症狀明顯減輕，術後第三天便順利康復出院。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"822160670932b7935f176f7da0438b16153c4d38","tid":2375181,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f0296f2659f173c3c318a9f4be03bccc3ea461","tid":2375181,"uid":204533,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:43:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210121/PYTGKGMMRNDL3AXBWQIZNZQEO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210121%2FPYTGKGMMRNDL3AXBWQIZNZQEO4%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=673dd734\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210121%2FPYTGKGMMRNDL3AXBWQIZNZQEO4%2F&h=53e74102\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210121/PYTGKGMMRNDL3AXBWQIZNZQEO4/</a>"},{"pid":"fc7d022899edc5b1c8d20a1731d913f9cb95df9d","tid":2375181,"uid":13303,"like":146,"dislike":2,"score":144,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:48:11.000Z","msg":"西隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54384ff04c699cb6e537194cf2e45d02e9f3a36","tid":2375181,"uid":253016,"like":517,"dislike":2,"score":515,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:49:11.000Z","msg":"不慎??"},{"pid":"1de7c5ae0c4fce2e2ee2edc5230efcd16cb77b7d","tid":2375181,"uid":47674,"like":228,"dislike":1,"score":227,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"「數名醫生上下其手，一起發力」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c2d152bc8ed460ecc00beebefa83e47b7104f4","tid":2375181,"uid":323849,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"quote":{"pid":"e54384ff04c699cb6e537194cf2e45d02e9f3a36","tid":2375181,"uid":253016,"like":517,"dislike":2,"score":515,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:49:11.000Z