"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b58f4953565f813a31bef551f2ea06a2b90615","tid":2375181,"uid":245819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7b5686413d539078e9d42098908c5fe79c11722","tid":2375181,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"近日，家住河南駐馬店市平輿縣的老畢，不慎將一個24cm&times;6cm大小的玻璃瓶塞入肛門，在家中苦苦努力一夜，不但沒把玻璃瓶取出，反而導致玻璃瓶越陷越深的情況下，被家人送往駐馬店市中心醫院肛腸科。醫生檢查後發現老畢的肛門不僅出現了明顯水腫，更可怕的是手指已經觸摸不到玻璃瓶；這意味著，單從肛門取出玻璃瓶的可能性微乎其微。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/OnmlAWtxyMqGFpbu2zWKMmhG1zk=/760x879/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XEIJJPZ6J5G45I2MO3YVZLKQGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOnmlAWtxyMqGFpbu2zWKMmhG1zk%3D%2F760x879%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXEIJJPZ6J5G45I2MO3YVZLKQGA.jpg&h=c75ac07c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最終，經過和家屬溝通協調，制定手術方案，商定在麻醉醫師的配合下，先自肛門處小心嘗試取出異物，如果取出困難，立刻為患者實施開腹手術，自腹部取出異物。在麻醉科手術部的密切配合下，由團隊中手尺寸最小的副主任醫師自肛門探查玻璃瓶的大概位置，發現玻璃瓶位於直腸乙狀結腸交界處，隨後在患者腹部輕柔擠壓腸管，將玻璃瓶緩慢推向直腸末端。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/t1T5wa63vXTEZv2uK1DA-P3USiw=/760x903/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZYLGCMW5WFBB3FHBHHC3TQHH7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft1T5wa63vXTEZv2uK1DA-P3USiw%3D%2F760x903%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZYLGCMW5WFBB3FHBHHC3TQHH7U.jpg&h=e91e40f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一組醫生透過肛門撐開器將患者的肛門撐開，觸摸到玻璃瓶後，用手術器械將其輕柔地向外牽拉，數名醫生上下其手，一起發力，歷經一個多小將其成功取出，避免了開腹手術，減輕了患者的創傷。術後第二天，老畢的不適症狀明顯減輕，術後第三天便順利康復出院。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Do4qugx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDo4qugx.gif&h=32aeeacd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a442d77ce6c26fd7c278fd4de2ddadeb7d67cb4","tid":2375181,"uid":245819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dae7ecece296de082fc8a0bdb693d86f1034fe9","tid":2375181,"uid":380450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d911dac4fada43cbc5800d5034666de3ee78fc82","tid":2375181,"uid":53119,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"c2513654a1caf0b3c8fe21182784ac1675655dbc","tid":2375181,"uid":340192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T00:47:34.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見 仲有冇人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"第一代高登Gay佬<br />\n我反而覺得撚撚真係無可取代~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"賭撚改圖集"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"Kuma wong嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31920e9eed9e4f63fa1324fa1c9a9afe1e56f43b","tid":2375181,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"「不慎」？佢當人係傻？"},{"pid":"5fada8f3ccb23e066b3c63815769fda91f35e727","tid":2375181,"uid":380450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a442d77ce6c26fd7c278fd4de2ddadeb7d67cb4","tid":2375181,"uid":245819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dae7ecece296de082fc8a0bdb693d86f1034fe9","tid":2375181,"uid":380450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d911dac4fada43cbc5800d5034666de3ee78fc82","tid":2375181,"uid":53119,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"第一代高登Gay佬<br />\n我反而覺得撚撚真係無可取代~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"賭撚改圖集"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20